        public void TitleBoundaries()
                     throws UserIDMustBeAtLeastEightCharactersException,
                            TitleTooLongException
        if title is longer than 30 chars, should raise TitleTooLongException. if title is less than or equal to 30 chars, it should not raise TitleTooLongException. the other two cases are fail states.
